  "body": "### Description\n\nI want Hibernate to collect statistics. I have a reproducer [here](https://github.com/t1/quarkus-hibernate-statistics-test-demo). Currently I have to configure:\r\n\r\n`quarkus.hibernate-orm.unsupported-properties.\"hibernate.generate_statistics\" = true`\r\n\r\nAs it's suggested for `unsupported-properties`, it would be nicer to have explicit support.\r\n\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\n Something like this:\r\n\r\n`quarkus.hibernate-orm.generate-statistics = true`",
